Titolo: Hopeless Masquerade

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Touhou Shinkirō ~ Hopeless Masquerade (Japanese: 東方心綺楼　～ Hopeless Masquerade, lit. "Eastern Tower of Heart Fabric") is a  versus fighting game in the Touhou Project game series, announced on 5 October 2012. The game, by Twilight Frontier and Team Shanghai Alice, is labelled as the 13.5th Touhou game. The final version of the game was released on 26 May 2013 at Reitaisai 10.